original_title: Brooklyn: New Lots Avenue - Newport Street
text:
(1)
New Lots Road, south side, between Newport Street and Church Ave., showing the home of William Ryerson, which was demolished in 1927. A 4-story apartment (No. 466 Rockaway Ave.), house occupied this site in 1929.
August 1924.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(2)
The same, a rear view.
August 1924.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(3)
The same, another rear view.
March 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
